HEADWORD: Inversely
<hw>In*verse"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an inverse
order or manner; by inversion; -- opposed to
<contr>directly</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Inversely proportional</b></col>. <cd>See <cref>Directly
